# THE PLATONIC APPENDIX: THE 10-24-26 INVARIANTS

*Register 1: The Verification Ledger*

This appendix provides the technical data required to verify the structural integrity of the **Platonic Verses**. It documents the **Invariants** that exist at the bedrock of the human interface.

## I. THE CORE TRIADS (Similarity Scaling)

The following triads represent the stable geometric "Agreements" used to build the world from domestic to imperial scale.

| Level | Triad (a-b-c) | Pythagorean Check ($a^2 + b^2 = c^2$) | Social Application |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
